The paper deals with exploring and filtering data, which is a common theme in database research (cs.DB). The use of a classifier to determine interesting categorical attributes is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Finally, the user study aspect of the evaluation suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
